{"tid":371434,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"屋企人淨係錫個仔","createTime":"2017-08-23T16:41:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-07T16:11:55.000Z","uid":102171,"like":5,"dislike":61,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"bc403745a48bbc3ca5d1bb1e62229ba36ca8f398","tid":371434,"uid":102171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T16:41:23.000Z","msg":"岩岩同完屋企鬧大交 好想離開呢個屋企<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我有個細佬<br />\n個細佬係屋企不嬲都好串<br />\n我屋企不嬲一直都錫個仔既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n 岩岩真係好嬲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n話說屋企人爸媽家姐都訓左教<br />\n咁我同細佬就係廳做自己野 <br />\n<br />\n因為我部電腦突然用唔到earphone<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁我就試下唔用earphone但開細聲段錄音黎聽下<br />\n點知呢個時候 我細佬就出聲<br />\n細佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好嘈呀 你唔識用earphone聽嫁咩？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />下 我已經開到好細聲嫁啦喎<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />你聾既唔代表我聾 你開聲好騷擾<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />點嘈到你呀？一係你返房囉<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我點解要返房 而家係你嘈 （跟住無啦啦話我冇返工冇用）<br />\n<br />\n去到呢到我做家姐自然開始炆啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 前排我岩岩quit左份full time因為覺得唔岩自己同人工低 所以而家都搵緊工 同埋學自己想學既野錄音果啲<br />\n<br />\n見到細佬個樣串串供仲要無大無細<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我做家姐緊係要管下佢啦 <br />\n我好細聲咁鬧唔想嘈到屋企人 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n點知我細佬愈鬧愈大聲 <br />\n佢舉動係想嘈醒曬屋企人 因為佢知佢地會幫佢口<br />\n爸媽家姐出到廳指住我黎話 我就坐係到比佢地話<br />\n佢地錫細佬錫到出曬面都算 <br />\n每個月比3000蚊零用錢比細佬<br />\n一個中學生3000蚊零用錢仲多過我平時洗費<br />\n屋企都已經窮嫁啦 我以前1蚊零用錢都無嫁 <br />\n點知佢地仲話男仔係要用多啲錢既女仔用少啲<br />\n<br />\n平時細佬係屋企無大無細鬧老豆 而家我呢個家姐管教返佢竟然反比老豆老母鬧返轉頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n岩岩喊完好累 好似咩都我錯曬咁<br />\n生存左廿年 係屋企細佬唔尊重你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n屋企又唔會為我主持公道 只係識叫我搵工返工搵工<br />\n好想離開咁唔開心既地方<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5085aed98db8190e36bc5e3ea4a59701f4dd91e","tid":371434,"uid":58140,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T16:42:19.000Z","msg":"屋企重男輕女?"},{"pid":"2903fdb905174a4ae09343fd6c333a523c2e8679","tid":371434,"uid":102171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T16:45:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>屋企重男輕女?</blockquote><br />\n老豆老母不嬲都係行舊思想 追仔所以生左我呢個女出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e0c5a278c0c6b502bbd9759b8cc6bd3c83d49b9","tid":371434,"uid":73909,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T16:46:00.000Z","msg":"好慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c521fc9345384ed43ece6b88873316bd2c4064c4","tid":371434,"uid":20270,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T16:47:57.000Z","msg":"唔係親生？捱多兩年搵到個伴侶搬出去啦 跟住斷絕關係"},{"pid":"f750cd73c96dd5b9a516a9fa1614a6296d3b10b9","tid":371434,"uid":49642,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T16:48:17.000Z","msg":"都20年啦<br />\n真係想離開既都係2個方法啫<br />\n自己爭氣搵錢搬出去住<br />\n搵個好男人嫁出去"},{"pid":"7fb221c68711d220acd8157c06bd66961b0d35e7","tid":371434,"uid":72226,"like":7,"dislike":69,"score":-62,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T16:48:24.000Z","msg":"臭雞<br />\n屋企人唔識將就下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8db5f0108139c2551c30a3fa9d39abd588683d10","tid":371434,"uid":102171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T16:49:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔係親生？捱多兩年搵到個伴侶搬出去啦 跟住斷絕關係</blockquote><br />\n我都覺得我唔係佢地親生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb6a3163d6beb5ed63a7b066856510ac3ff4bc09","tid":371434,"uid":72226,"like":13,"dislike":3,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T16:49:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>臭雞<br />\n屋企人唔識將就下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n呢個世界從來都冇公平呢兩個字<br />\n第1日出嚟呢個世界玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85cfc332832687f7367178e305e370b6573fcdda","tid":371434,"uid":102171,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T16:50:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>臭雞<br />\n屋企人唔識將就下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n平時屋企人多 都係等到夜晚我先可以做自己野"},{"pid":"657d4b8f23e81b116c610881720f38956722ef46","tid":371434,"uid":102171,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T16:53:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>都20年啦<br />\n真係想離開既都係2個方法啫<br />\n自己爭氣搵錢搬出去住<br />\n搵個好男人嫁出去</blockquote><br />\n草緊錢啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />但呢個時勢 上車又難 租屋又草唔到錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5524e41d745fbe395d7f0b81ec2429ac4fc65eb1","tid":371434,"uid":16273,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T16:53:59.000Z","msg":"同你調轉晒，我都係有家姐，但屋企重女輕男，老母肯比錢家姐買樓，但同我就講有本事自己先買"},{"pid":"6d2da488d79e641f0125e6a563b32cce9bf98812","tid":371434,"uid":36065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T16:54:39.000Z","msg":"有能力搬走之餘 脫離埋父母親關係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6adb70f9988b91f983ad80b4b7b2c2a71c8d2ea1","tid":371434,"uid":57186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T16:56:19.000Z","msg":"好慘,深表同情,愛莫能助"},{"pid":"290f7fc1b50a7fb1b481656eb9addc8807f599a2","tid":371434,"uid":49642,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T16:57:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>都20年啦<br />\n真係想離開既都係2個方法啫<br />\n自己爭氣搵錢搬出去住<br />\n搵個好男人嫁出去</blockquote><br />\n草緊錢啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />但呢個時勢 上車又難 租屋又草唔到錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n你唔係財技驚人或者有橫財運既<br />\n上車就唔好諗啦，儲到你30歲都未夠首期<br />\n我儲左8年都未夠<br />\n<br />\n你想自力搬走既只有租樓"},{"pid":"bd28ccd89051db1ea0af68bfebb336fe58e05845","tid":371434,"uid":139676,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T16:57:49.000Z","msg":"比個機會我照顧你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"770338918dde61d3e50b57010b1118183b32705e","tid":371434,"uid":102171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T16:58:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>同你調轉晒，我都係有家姐，但屋企重女輕男，老母肯比錢家姐買樓，但同我就講有本事自己先買</blockquote><br />\n我屋企應該有錢都留比細佬啦 <br />\n平時一到出糧果日就問我拎家用<br />\n遲左幾日就會問我出左糧未<br />\n平時我省住省住用錢<br />\n個細佬用咁多錢佢地就幫曬佢口<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5448d09313c791827be72fb0e2164e15e39a5a7e","tid":371434,"uid":100322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T17:00:29.000Z","msg":"我屋企都係<br />\n已經理所當然咁偏心<br />\n自己搵到錢搬出去住"},{"pid":"7b0ec6ff6f5e2025c62899c77a068ce366d5fb55","tid":371434,"uid":102171,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T17:01:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有能力搬走之餘 脫離埋父母親關係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔想脫離關係 畢竟佢地都係親生父母<br />\n其實我都想盡孝既<br />\n只不過屋企無人會理我感受<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b69dd37eff1c7f75596edc874837e18f9667b27c","tid":371434,"uid":69946,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T17:02:34.000Z","msg":"得閒過黎訓，我都係咁頂唔住搬左出黎<br />\n利申：有兩個家姐一個細佬，一同佢地嘈，兩老即屌我"},{"pid":"d445e0744abd32864cf13882fdd63b9d79c357fb","tid":371434,"uid":102171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T17:03:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我屋企都係<br />\n已經理所當然咁偏心<br />\n自己搵到錢搬出去住</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />家家有本難念的經"},{"pid":"7d63b33c1ef17d89f11ff92464c42471d4599c05","tid":371434,"uid":40908,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T17:04:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>有能力搬走之餘 脫離埋父母親關係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔想脫離關係 畢竟佢地都係親生父母<br />\n其實我都想盡孝既<br />\n只不過屋企無人會理我感受<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n愚孝抵你比屋企人蝦<br />\n收番個post繼續比佢地恰啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e45c63879a81b6b6ab7b2b5594956570f55983c","tid":371434,"uid":71175,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T17:05:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>都20年啦<br />\n真係想離開既都係2個方法啫<br />\n自己爭氣搵錢搬出去住<br />\n搵個好男人嫁出去</blockquote><br />\n草緊錢啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />但呢個時勢 上車又難 租屋又草唔到錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n你唔係財技驚人或者有橫財運既<br />\n上車就唔好諗啦，儲到你30歲都未夠首期<br />\n我儲左8年都未夠<br />\n<br />\n你想自力搬走既只有租樓</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我儲左 7年 有1.5M無話唔得ge"},{"pid":"1c574b3f2e38b93f05e272c90a2ca9f50e7ef60a","tid":371434,"uid":74081,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T17:07:25.000Z","msg":"完全明白你感受<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你試下好認真咁同佢地講下你嘅感受啦 不過就真係唔撚洗同你個on9細佬講道理啦 屌你老味 自己親家姐都唔可以讓下 小小野就要出動老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 幾多歲呀？我真係覺得宜家香港啲細路越來越冇禮貌又自大 屋企啲人個個都寵到佢地仆街 係時候你要屌醒你細佬啦 <br />\n如果你屋企人又再不分青紅皂白就話你 我覺得你真係要慢慢逐個咁同佢地講下佢地有咩問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85a50625b3b2d5f1b12f0e5bd54e6748df509c2d","tid":371434,"uid":121029,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T17:07:26.000Z","msg":"老婆屋企人重男輕女<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b99d788e9da27df00ea93fa41bc9936f64d7bbb","tid":371434,"uid":102171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T17:07:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>得閒過黎訓，我都係咁頂唔住搬左出黎<br />\n利申：有兩個家姐一個細佬，一同佢地嘈，兩老即屌我</blockquote><br />\n你自己一個搬出黎?租屋住定點？"},{"pid":"ad1f5d22a102b5d459e4a310a515e3e79e273c43","tid":371434,"uid":49642,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T17:08:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>都20年啦<br />\n真係想離開既都係2個方法啫<br />\n自己爭氣搵錢搬出去住<br />\n搵個好男人嫁出去</blockquote><br />\n草緊錢啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />但呢個時勢 上車又難 租屋又草唔到錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n你唔係財技驚人或者有橫財運既<br />\n上車就唔好諗啦，儲到你30歲都未夠首期<br />\n我儲左8年都未夠<br />\n<br />\n你想自力搬走既只有租樓</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我儲左 7年 有1.5M無話唔得ge</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n巴打利害<br />\n但樓主唔似想忍多7年喎"},{"pid":"31844e528d173f88b832af7bd3b73ffedbef6b77","tid":371434,"uid":42379,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T17:09:13.000Z","msg":"你廿幾歲先？你細佬又幾多歲？<br />\n中學就有3k零用錢 痴線"},{"pid":"e197c4e116bf137f59614873ccb58922b75b6104","tid":371434,"uid":102171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T17:10:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>完全明白你感受<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你試下好認真咁同佢地講下你嘅感受啦 不過就真係唔撚洗同你個on9細佬講道理啦 屌你老味 自己親家姐都唔可以讓下 小小野就要出動老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 幾多歲呀？我真係覺得宜家香港啲細路越來越冇禮貌又自大 屋企啲人個個都寵到佢地仆街 係時候你要屌醒你細佬啦 <br />\n如果你屋企人又再不分青紅皂白就話你 我覺得你真係要慢慢逐個咁同佢地講下佢地有咩問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n講過了 佢地都依舊係咁 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"806419db5e90bfa951089e02e133de1573d27b66","tid":371434,"uid":102171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T17:13:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>都20年啦<br />\n真係想離開既都係2個方法啫<br />\n自己爭氣搵錢搬出去住<br />\n搵個好男人嫁出去</blockquote><br />\n草緊錢啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />但呢個時勢 上車又難 租屋又草唔到錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n你唔係財技驚人或者有橫財運既<br />\n上車就唔好諗啦，儲到你30歲都未夠首期<br />\n我儲左8年都未夠<br />\n<br />\n你想自力搬走既只有租樓</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我儲左 7年 有1.5M無話唔得ge</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n巴打利害<br />\n但樓主唔似想忍多7年喎</blockquote><br />\n岩岩畢業出黎 要儲既話真係要幾年時間<br />\n我而家就想即刻走 不過可以走得去邊又可以走到幾多日呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b24d036c7ab2d0685978e39674c6cf3ca65c912","tid":371434,"uid":102171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T17:14:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你廿幾歲先？你細佬又幾多歲？<br />\n中學就有3k零用錢 痴線</blockquote><br />\n23了 佢16歲<br />\n我返工每月洗費都無3000蚊因為我好省要儲錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a0672739e4419e9a9370844c735fe4078bc2393","tid":371434,"uid":49642,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T17:16:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>都20年啦<br />\n真係想離開既都係2個方法啫<br />\n自己爭氣搵錢搬出去住<br />\n搵個好男人嫁出去</blockquote><br />\n草緊錢啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />但呢個時勢 上車又難 租屋又草唔到錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n你唔係財技驚人或者有橫財運既<br />\n上車就唔好諗啦，儲到你30歲都未夠首期<br />\n我儲左8年都未夠<br />\n<br />\n你想自力搬走既只有租樓</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我儲左 7年 有1.5M無話唔得ge</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n巴打利害<br />\n但樓主唔似想忍多7年喎</blockquote><br />\n岩岩畢業出黎 要儲既話真係要幾年時間<br />\n我而家就想即刻走 不過可以走得去邊又可以走到幾多日呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n至少等你儲到半年生活費(租，食，行，日用) <br />\n再加有份穩定工作就可以走啦<br />\n決心就睇你自己既啫，無人幫到你"},{"pid":"e5d4d6baee1c98dcfccb0ea3ad802a13242eee7c","tid":371434,"uid":130162,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T17:17:02.000Z","msg":"same here<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9fc87ffe36f927777d1b229db16b75777f9bc8e7","tid":371434,"uid":42379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T17:19:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>你廿幾歲先？你細佬又幾多歲？<br />\n中學就有3k零用錢 痴線</blockquote><br />\n23了 佢16歲<br />\n我返工每月洗費都無3000蚊因為我好省要儲錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n16歲就咁牙擦，大咗仲得了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11a6cf1c95851825b5419f6ee5c4178c999441a8","tid":371434,"uid":58140,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T17:20:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>你廿幾歲先？你細佬又幾多歲？<br />\n中學就有3k零用錢 痴線</blockquote><br />\n23了 佢16歲<br />\n我返工每月洗費都無3000蚊因為我好省要儲錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n16歲就咁牙擦，大咗仲得了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n屋企人寵得太勁反而害左佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nbtw 宜家啲00後真係呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b65f0d85fabc6d317e07cc181660f0f1c25b0d3","tid":371434,"uid":50870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T17:21:16.000Z","msg":"好慘 唔知點安慰你<br />\n上面都有人講左 要自己努力加油 儲錢搬走<br />\n唔洗畀家用佢地 養自己就夠啦"},{"pid":"ec137e91e9d7a4999a251f9d28aed28eb841dc00","tid":371434,"uid":130162,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T17:21:29.000Z","msg":"咪撚俾家用 同人夾租搬岀去啦"},{"pid":"7ecf7eb8d2b6865b766a0697fc3b3df5aa478c87","tid":371434,"uid":111625,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T17:22:41.000Z","msg":"樓豬你幾歲先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n屋企人關唔關心你先,如果唔關心既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n每個月扔低幾千銀 比老豆老母咪算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔明點解要比咁多錢細佬,種壞哂個仆街仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我屋企得我一粒仔,但老豆老母都日日煩鳩住我,好唔得你好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但又讀緊書無能力搬出去,平時一返到屋企我就帶撚住個耳機,直接無視佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9f13b956a58e0aab785bf0f271f8bb560c8f50e","tid":371434,"uid":118721,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T17:25:56.000Z","msg":"最撚憎<br />\n遲早個仆街仔敗撚哂屋企d 錢<br />\n我屋企都係重男輕女<br />\n垃圾！"},{"pid":"75b2f7637e602b34eb1e2d2fa6400126fd684d52","tid":371434,"uid":118721,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T17:27:00.000Z","msg":"絲打<br />\n我係你拿拿聲搵個好對象<br />\n之後結婚搬出黎住<br />\n佢有房而屋企唔介意就2個一齊住住先<br />\n機會留比有準備ge 人"},{"pid":"05cbce770a7550e5cd1f73f887ee593fced31e2a","tid":371434,"uid":1935,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T17:46:19.000Z","msg":"唔好俾咁多家用<br />\n<br />\n平時咪無視下佢地<br />\n自己好過d"},{"pid":"909c785f69413161b65629c9fee7da9de4d844bd","tid":371434,"uid":137997,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T17:48:49.000Z","msg":"貼你細佬張圖上來問題即刻有好轉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d516c71d9a90f524e04dded2c4bc98ef1b64dcd0","tid":371434,"uid":57378,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T17:53:55.000Z","msg":"重男輕女有咩問題？"},{"pid":"06ac421af58e7ea3d3372195bcbed1ff9fdf1948","tid":371434,"uid":34714,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T17:56:05.000Z","msg":"我屋企錫女多d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77bcb9c8a79c2e8245ee3f5db2e584b9a1b3cc72","tid":371434,"uid":34714,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T17:56:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>你廿幾歲先？你細佬又幾多歲？<br />\n中學就有3k零用錢 痴線</blockquote><br />\n23了 佢16歲<br />\n我返工每月洗費都無3000蚊因為我好省要儲錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n差咁多咪讓下佢囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3da0887537bb51aa5bfc7130853b2b7b1d271621","tid":371434,"uid":94444,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T18:00:58.000Z","msg":"3000禁多 絲打試下申請公屋？ 一係搵fd一齊租間屋企？"},{"pid":"0d254aac20a22d9c43042a69bbe6c97ab09141fb","tid":371434,"uid":33131,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T18:02:56.000Z","msg":"學gone girl 條女咁<br />\n由而家開始寫日記<br />\n鐘意可以補番之前既日子<br />\n一日一日咁暗示比屋企人/細佬虐待<br />\n之後搵日同細佬鬧交，就撞自己個頭埋牆角 / 搵野打腫自己隻眼<br />\n最後報警拉你細佬坐監<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ad18c7e835848a9f532222726f9ec48d104a01a","tid":371434,"uid":28721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T18:02:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>有能力搬走之餘 脫離埋父母親關係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔想脫離關係 畢竟佢地都係親生父母<br />\n其實我都想盡孝既<br />\n只不過屋企無人會理我感受<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n愚孝抵你比屋企人蝦<br />\n收番個post繼續比佢地恰啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n岩阿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc1434c6267c5df9d324daf315ae24e8fd9baba4","tid":371434,"uid":132674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T18:05:31.000Z","msg":"真係要 屌你老豆老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3fa07fc1ea96bbc0e9d19147fbfabf6eb0ee6ec2","tid":371434,"uid":93069,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T18:05:42.000Z","msg":"好明白樓主 我都有差唔多嘅經歷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但係咩都做唔到 只可以同你講句共勉之"},{"pid":"e411d288e1a2404e1c44798078fa2f121fd8c7fa","tid":371434,"uid":97393,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T18:08:14.000Z","msg":"你家用交幾錢？ 如果係3000嘅就同你老竇老母講<br />\n以後你家用直接當係你細佬零用咁出啦 <br />\n咁佢最少睇錢份上會尊重你啲 <br />\n<br />\n而且你唔gur可以唔畀 <br />\n就話唔係想走家用數 係你細佬太無大無細 要佢同你道歉 <br />\n一句sorry就有錢收 你老竇老母都會息事寧人叫你細佬服軟 久而久之修正你細佬嘅態度<br />\n<br />\n但我覺得最重要係你要企硬立場 <br />\n你屋企人對你唔好佢哋唔會有自覺 可能仲覺得有啖飯畀你食你已經要謝主隆恩<br />\n你心入面可以想唔斷絕關係 但最少你表面上要有寧為玉碎嘅態度 咁先有返啲籌碼<br />\n<br />\n講真 如果你屋企真係著緊你 <br />\n你口講一世唔返嚟 出去住返一兩個月 佢哋絕對淆過你 驚你唔夠錢使驚你畀人呃乜乜柒<br />\n如果覺得無所謂嘅 咁你都算睇清楚你父母 畀個機會自己唔好再愚孝"},{"pid":"b324ae28c7fe98f4204bb34d1d6a00e9f635ffe8","tid":371434,"uid":86753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T18:10:24.000Z","msg":"絲打我同你差唔多不過仲嚴重 岩岩差啲搞到人命都冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72d6a7274e0a9e6a20a6b1dc1c52b073b0caa12f","tid":371434,"uid":105522,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T18:11:52.000Z","msg":"俾家用俾少3000囉<br />\n同你父母講 份家用唔包細佬果份<br />\n叫佢有手有腳自己出去揾錢"},{"pid":"9dc8b10cc184915bc2df1e8bae62317b2a8ccecf","tid":371434,"uid":29077,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T18:28:59.000Z","msg":"3000蚊圍返條數都喺一日100 食兩餐都無咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f644b7b453dfe5b204eecc45b9d69e5c45414b1","tid":371434,"uid":43061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T18:40:29.000Z","msg":"16歲3000蚊零月錢<br />\n屋企人寵到佢仆街 大個仲死得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b52904cd54db46350c8d94c1590df64018d4780e","tid":371434,"uid":59528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T18:43:29.000Z","msg":"同男朋友搬出去住<br />\n當自己無老豆老母<br />\n不過我都幾肯定你做唔出"},{"pid":"3ab2481fe796f5eb329eddefeffc328ebd9c8f19","tid":371434,"uid":14190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T18:52:39.000Z","msg":"3000蚊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我